      "label": "Configure Buttons",
      "icon": "fa-magic",
      "description": "Each button below shows its current value. To set one: click 'Configure', then press that physical button on the unit twice to confirm. To unmap a button: click its 'Configure', then click 'Clear Selected Button'. If you set a button to a value already used by another, the other is reassigned automatically. Use 'Capture Base Resistance' to record the resting value while pressing nothing. Make all your changes, then click 'Save & Restart Controls' to apply them at once.",
