      "icon": "fa-sliders",
      "description": "Advanced/manual setup. Most users should use 'Configure Buttons (Capture)' above instead. Turn on the switch to edit the raw channel/value mappings by hand. Enter as channel, value (e.g. 0, 12); a range like 0, 24-25 is also allowed.",
